snippet.title: FINAL FANTASY X/X-2 HD Remaster | Tidus and Yuna
snippet.description:
Preorder Now: https://sqex.link/X704

The story of Tidus & Yuna begins on Xbox One and Nintendo Switch, April 16th 2019. FINAL FANTASY X/X-2 HD Remaster includes FINAL FANTASY X, FINAL FANTASY X Eternal Calm, FINAL FANTASY X-2, FINAL FANTASY X-2 LAST MISSION, Credits & Bonus Audio Drama.
